You cannot eat a doughnut and walk backwards on a city street. <br>
<br>
McDonald:<br>
Your goose may not be paraded down Main Street. <br>
<br>
North Canton:<br>
It is against the law to roller skate without notifying the police. <br>
<br>
Oxford:<br>
It's illegal for a woman to strip off her clothing while standing in front of a man's picture. <br>
<br>
Paulding:<br>
A policeman may bite a dog to quiet him. <br>
